sources.description: HIGHEST QUALITY ENGLISH VERSION AVAILABLE! BACKGROUND NOTES:  This movie was originally meant to be released on Thankgiving in the USA in 1988, but was postponed to 1991 due to New World Pictures going bankrupt. Development began in 1985 and work was done in Europe in 1986 and 1987. Plot:  In another dimension, the villainous scientist Duke of Zill, with the help of his mechanical, geometric army, takes over the Land of Oriana, prompting Felix the Cat to save its princess and restore order once again. THIS IS A COLLABORATION OF THE FOLLOWING COUNTRIES United States Germany Hungary Poland Bulgaria Canada
